Itemized Passive Description:
*Basic effect(s)*
- Ki +2 and ATK & DEF 200%{passiveImg:up_g}
*For 5 turn(s) from the character's entry turn*
- Ki +2 and ATK 100%{passiveImg:up_g}
*For every Ki when attacking*
- ATK & DEF 10%{passiveImg:up_g} (up to 180%)
*When attacking with 18 or more Ki*
- Guards all attacks
- Launches an additional Super Attack
*When all allies attacking in the same turn have obtained a
Ki Sphere*
- All allies' DEF 10%{passiveImg:up_g} (self excluded) per Ki obtained by the
character himself (count starts from the 18th Ki)
*When the name of an ally who is attacking in the same turn or
an enemy includes "Goku" (Youth, Captain Ginyu, Jr., etc.
excluded)*
- Ki +4 and ATK & DEF 59%{passiveImg:up_g}
*When there is a "Majin Buu Saga" Category ally whose name
includes "Goku" attacking in the same turn*
- Ki +4 and ATK & DEF 59%{passiveImg:up_g}
